summary: I had a few presets just getting dust in my game. Decided to share with you.
descriptionHtml:
[size=5][b]A Pack of Presets

[/b][/size]This pack contains 9 Racemenu presets, all female characters. 
Feel free to modify each character as you wish. I'd love to see them in your game, so screenshots are welcome.

(English is not my native language, I'm sorry)
